<body>
    <h1>How to Install Node.js</h1>
    <p>Follow these steps to install Node.js on your computer:</p>
    <ol>
        <li>download the installer from the <a href="#" onclick="openLink('https://nodejs.org/')">Node.js official website</a> or use the direct download link below.</li>
        <li>Run the installer and follow the on-screen instructions.</li>
        <li>don't select the <b>chocolatey</b> checkbox as it's not needed for this project.</li>
        <li>After installation, search for <b>node.js</b> in your applications to check if Node.js is installed.</li>
    </ol>
    <button onclick="openLink('https://nodejs.org/dist/v14.16.0/node-v14.16.0-x64.msi')">Node.js Download Link</button>
